  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nolahdehts buhſi tu ee-\needains/ un nolahdehts buhſi tu\niſeedains.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS fuhtihs\nſtarp tew to Nolahdehtanu/\nDumpi un Nomaitaſchanu/eekſch\nwiﬀa/ pee ka tu tawu Rohku iſ-\nſteepi/ ko tu darri/ teekams tu te-\ndeldehts tohpi/ un teekams tu pa-\npreeſchu bohjā etj/ tawu taunu\nDarbu deht/ ka tu no mannim\neſſi atſtahjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS liks tew to\nMehri peeſipt/ teekams wiſsch tew\niſdelde no tahs Semmes/us kur-\nren tu eij wiꞥſsu eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS jittihs tew\nar Tuhkumu/ un ar Drudſi/ un\nar Karſoni/ un karstahm Sehr-\ngahm/ un ar Sohbinu/ un ar\nBullasLaiku/ un ar Ruhfu/ kas\ntew wajahs/ kamehr tu bohjā eij.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tawa Debbes/kas pahr\ntawu Galwu irr buhs ka Warsch/\nun ta Seimme/ kas tawā Appak-\nſchā/ buhs ka Dſelse.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS dohs ta-\nwai Semmel Pihſchlus un Vel-\nnus Leetus Weetā/no Debbes no-\nnahks tas pahr tew/ teekams tu iſ-\ndeldehts tohpi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS dohs tew/\nka tu tohpi nokauts preeſsch ta-\nweem Eenaidneekeem/ pa weenu\nZeltu iſeeti tu prett wiꞥſneem/ un\npa feptizeem Zetteem behgſi tu no\nwiꞥſneem/ un tu tapſi no wiſſahmi\nSemmes Walstibahm iſkaitihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tawa nomtrufi Mee-\nfa buhs par Ehdeenu wiﬀeem Put-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS jittihs tew\nar Egiptes Tuhkumeem/ un ar\nPakfatas Sehrgahm/ un ar\nKraupi/ un ar Naisu/ kas ne warr\ndſcedinata tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS jittihs tew\nar Trakſumu/ un ar Aklibu/ un\nar Sirde Stulbibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tu puſs Deena grabb-\nſtifi itt ka weens Aklajs grabbsta\nKrehſlibā/ un tawi Zelti ne labbi\niſdobſees/ bet tu buhſi tikſai no-\nſpatdihts un nolaupihts wiſſu\nMuhſchu/ un Iſglahbeja ne buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu faderreſi tew weenu\nSeewu/ bet zits gullehs pee wiſ-\nkas/ tu uſtaisift wcenu Namnu/\nun ne dſihwoſi eekſch ta/ tu deh-\nſtifi weenu Wihna-Dahrsu/ bet\ntu ne baudiſi wiſſa Augſus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Taws Wehrſis taps\npreeſsch tawahm Azzim nokauts/\nbet tu ne ehdiſi no ta/ taws Ehse-\nlis taps preeſsch tawahm Azzim\nar Warru nemts/ un ue taps tew\natdohts/ tawi fiſki Lobpi taps ta-\nweem Eenaidneekeem nodohti/ un\nne weena Iſglahbeja ne buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawi Dehti un tawas\nMettas taps kahdai zittai Tan-\ntai nodohti/ ka tawas Azzis to\nredſ/ un fanihks pahr winneem ik-\ndeenas/ bet tawā Rohkā Spehka\nne buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawas Semmes Augſus/\nun wiﬀu tawu Padohmu ehdihs\nweena Tauta/ ko tu ne pasihtsi/\n"
    }
  ],
